{"tid":251483,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"求漫畫名","createTime":"2017-05-21T03:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T04:39:04.000Z","uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f37d299d4ec5017d00ed4d1a3171c12b8afbaca4","tid":251483,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"早排睇過有套漫畫唔記得左個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求各位幫忙<br />\n<br />\n劇情講男主自細同個Frd習武 1X歲去申請做國家騎士團之類 王道漫黎好似<br />\n<br />\n點知個frd就入左最勁最高級個團 男主就入左名氣最差最桀驁不馴個團 入面得6-7個隊友個團長係個大叔黎<br />\n<br />\n跟著好似劇情差唔多係咁上下做下任務果D 好似有幕係男主出城做任務撞到佢個frd及其團友 個團友笑主角入左廢團無鬼用但最後主角救左條友一命咁上下"},{"pid":"22daaedc5fed691e05a4e3df29b8fcbe058fbbec","tid":251483,"uid":18526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"黑色五葉草？"},{"pid":"a8b9dad983a0705bd423ac15eaeff07795f511be","tid":251483,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑色五葉草？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}